- 7 Supabase tables (customers, inventory, orders, invoices, payments, documents, conversations) with RLS
- 7 API routes: dashboard, inventory search/export, order placement with BOL generation, billing/payments, AI chat (OpenAI + fallback), notifications, external API endpoint
- 8 portal pages: dashboard (Recharts charts, KPIs), inventory browser (table/card, filters, cart), place order (multi-step with BOL preview), order history (timeline, tracking), receiving (photos, QC), billing (auto-pay, payment modal), AI support chat, settings (API keys, notifications)
- 6 shared components: PortalNav (sidebar/mobile), PortalChat, CartSidebar, PaymentModal, DocumentUpload, PhotoGallery
- DOT-compliant BOL generator with freight class calculation
- Comprehensive demo data: Mountain West Supplements, 16 SKUs, 6 orders, 12 months invoices
- Premium responsive design (desktop sidebar, mobile bottom nav)
